    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews klanfija ta\nPuifcha Balsi / un tas DEewa\nEngelis fauze Ahgari no Deb-\nbes / un fazzija us to : Kas tew\nfait / Ahgare ? ne bihstees / jo\nDEews irr ta Puifcha Balsi\nklanfijis / tai Weetâ / fur wiꞥsch\nirr/ zellees/ pazell to Puifi / un\nturri to stipri pee tawas Rohkas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es zelfschu winnu par\nweenu leelu Tautu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews atwehre win-\nnas Azzis/nn ta eeraudsija wee-\nnu Uhdens Akku / un gabje un\npildija to Tranku ar Uhdeni / un\ndsirdinaja to Puifi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un DEews bija ar to Puifi/\nun tas ange/ un dsihwoja Tuḱnefi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tappe Strehtnecks ar\nStohpu / un dsihwoja Waranas\nTuḱnefi / un winna Mahte neh-\nme tain weenu Seewu/ no Egip-\ntes-Semnes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tannâ Laikâ runnaja\nAbimeleks un Pihkols winna\nRarra-Spehka Wirfineeks ar Ab-\nbrämm/ fazzidami : DEews irr\nar tew wiḱnis Leetâs/ ko tu darri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nn fivehre man\ntan pee Deewa / ka tu ne g\nwiltigs buht prett mann/ jeb\nmanneem Behrneem/ nedß\nmanneem Behrnu· Behrne\npehz tahs Schehlastibas / t\npee tew darrijis / buhs ten\nman darriht/ un pee tahß E\nmes / furxâ tu weens Swe\nneeks bijiś.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrääms faz\nEs gribbu swehreht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbrääms norah\nAbimelekku / weenas Uhdens\nkas deht/ ko Abimeleka Kalp\nWarru bij nehmuschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Abime\nEs ne efimu finnajis/ kas fcho\ntu irr darrijis / ir tu man t\neffi pafazzijis / un es to ar n\ninn dsirdejis lihds fchoddeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms nehmu\nwis/ un Wehrschus / un i\ntohs Abimelekam/ un tee da\nabbee weenu Derribu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Ahbraäms lifke fe\nJehrus no Awini fewischki\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Abimelek\nAhbräamn:Par ko irr fchee fe\nJehri ? ko tu fewischkt effi li\n"
